{
  "stem": "14168.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, an announcement came, over the radio, that the President von Hindenburg-- who was the president of Germany at the time-- had called on Hitler to form a government.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't quite-- well, of course, we were scared.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we didn't, at that point, really realize what it meant.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Although some of our Christian or non-Jewish schoolmates said, ah, it's not going to be that bad.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now he's going to be called, called upon to take measures and not just to talk.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And maybe he's not going to be very effective.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But anyway, that-- I remember that day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the same evening, the Nazis, the storm troopers, came to the streets.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there was a-- there were demonstrations.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they walked down the streets, and the population was frantic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was in January, 1933.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it affected us to the extent that, of course, the economic-- general economic conditions became very, very bad.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so my father's business suffered, like everybody else's business suffered.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I remember, there were several things which contributed, of course, to people, A, blaming the Jews.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Number two, of course, calling on Hitler and receiving his message with enthusiasm.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A, the defeat-- the military defeat in 1918.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were looking for scapegoats.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there, of course, were the Jews and the Communists-- the stab in the back, and the Weimar Republic, which they claim was just a Jews' republic.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then came the severe economic downturn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Tremendous amount of unemployed people, I still remember the long lines in front of the state's dole offices, where doles were given to these people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so there was a polarization in Germany between the Communists on the one hand and the National Socialists, the Nazis, on the other.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
